description:
The UNF Mobile iOS app allows you to keep up-to-date with UNF news, take care of your University business and connect with others when and where it is convenient for you. You can do it all, right from the palm of your hand. 

Once installed, the app will get you quickly to the UNF website and access all your favorite links. At the same time, you can read all the latest news about UNF from our press releases, media hits, Osprey Update or the Alumni Journal.

UNF Mobile also allows you to customize the layout of the module icons in the app.  Simply press and hold any icon until they all wiggle, then move any of the icons to a new position (or even to a new page!) as desired , and touch the grid icon at the bottom of the page to return to normal mode.


Features:
 
Directory - Search the public directory for faculty members, staff members, administrators and departments. Place a call, find an office location on the UNF campus and save contact information right to your phone’s address book.

Events - Always know what’s happening at UNF. Browse academic as well as other types of events and quickly add them to your personal calendar.

Maps - Find out where you are and where you need to go.

News - Get the latest UNF news, including campus Alerts, Osprey Update, press releases and media coverage.

Emergency - Quickly access emergency phone numbers.

unf.edu: Find out about UNF, academics, admissions, campus life and more.

Learn – Get instant access to all of your Blackboard Learn™ courses on the go. Check grades, post to discussion forums, view important class announcements, read and download assignments, upload content and more.

Campus Tour Map - A virtual tour of the UNF campus.
